303
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,800
We agreed you'd look after Susu!

304
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,050
Don't you know what elders say?

305
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,660
When the baby hears

306
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:59,320
its father's voice often,

307
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,120
that little head grows sharper!

308
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:03,710
