312
00:12:13,540 --> 00:12:14,770
The Farmers' Association
in our valiage is established,

313
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:15,590
with Tietou leading it.

314
00:12:15,590 --> 00:12:16,320
And today,

315
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:19,590
Xiazhuang is holding a struggle session
against Pan Xiaogui.

316
00:12:19,590 --> 00:12:21,040
Tietou's taking the lead?

317
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:21,830
Perfect.

318
00:12:22,590 --> 00:12:23,470
I just got his land back

319
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:24,680
from Feng Er—

320
00:12:24,710 --> 00:12:26,310
let him farm it another year.

321
00:12:26,310 --> 00:12:27,790
He ought to be thanking me,

322
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,040
not causing trouble!

323
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:30,080
And...

324
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,200
that Pan Xiaogui?
Everybody knows what he is—

325
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,460
a straight-up tyrant!

326
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:34,920
To take revenge,

327
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,960
he dug up a tenant's ancestors' graves

328
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,230
and buried a donkey in their place.

329
00:12:38,230 --> 00:12:41,290
Also, he set dogs on anyone
who stepped near his fields!

330
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,280
A struggle session against him?

331
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,630
That's mercy.

332
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:44,280
Truth is—

333
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:46,410
a monster like that belongs in chains.

334
00:12:46,430 --> 00:12:48,350
Yes! You're absolutely right,
sister-in-law!

335
00:12:48,350 --> 00:12:49,990
And let's add another charge

336
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:50,740
to Pan Xiaogui's crimes—

337
00:12:50,740 --> 00:12:52,230
refusing to lower rents
and interest rates,

338
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:53,830
denying permanent tenancy!

339
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:56,250
That deserves double punishment!

340
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:59,520
Then what are you waiting for,
sister-in-law?

341
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,370
Round up the tenants—now!

342
00:13:01,370 --> 00:13:02,630
Ask them straight:
Lower rents and interest…

343
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:03,890
or permanent tenancy?

344
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:05,120
Why should I do that?

345
00:13:05,990 --> 00:13:06,400
Wait,

346
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:07,560
Wendian.

347
00:13:07,830 --> 00:13:09,160
