348
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,710
Why keep pushing me to lead this?

349
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:14,570
Just because you've dabbled
in new learning,

350
00:13:14,610 --> 00:13:16,550
now you're itching to overturn the world?

351
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:17,960
Should I go home and tell Father?

352
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,560
You think it's that easy?

353
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:21,280
If I'd known

354
00:13:21,710 --> 00:13:22,510
your new learning

355
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:23,750
would target

356
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:25,200
your own sister-in-law,

357
00:13:25,470 --> 00:13:27,400
I would never have let you study it!

358
00:13:36,930 --> 00:13:40,530
That was satisfying—
watching Pan Xiaogui get what he deserved!

359
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,250
What's so funny?

360
00:13:42,990 --> 00:13:44,830
Now you finally see
how we'll get things done back home, eh?

361
00:13:44,830 --> 00:13:45,760
What do you mean?

362
00:13:46,110 --> 00:13:48,080
How? Exactly like this—

363
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:50,810
starting with that old widow
of the Fei-Zuo clan!

364
00:13:51,370 --> 00:13:53,860
This Pan Xiaogui—wicked to the bone!

365
00:13:54,470 --> 00:13:56,690
Even grave-robbing wasn't beneath him,

366
00:13:56,690 --> 00:13:58,920
tormenting those
tenant farmers mercilessly.

367
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:01,440
But Mrs. Fei...
surely she'd never stoop that low?

368
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,860
The speaker just revealed
how Pan Xiaogui swindled villagers

369
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:05,170
out of their homes.

370
00:14:05,470 --> 00:14:07,320
While the homeless froze outside—

371
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,560
children dying of cold—

372
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:10,690
he feasted inside on the finest foods.

373
00:14:11,070 --> 00:14:13,230
Exactly! He even helped Zhang Zongchang
garrison troops—

374
00:14:13,230 --> 00:14:16,160
that scheme of collecting
four years' military grain tax in advance

375
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:17,490
was his brainchild too.

376
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:19,160
What a scourge!

377
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:20,710
Niu Wu is right,

378
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,800
but Mrs. Fei... she's no oppressor.

379
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:24,680
And you—

380
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,160
Didn't even askif she recognizes
the Farmers' Association,

381
00:14:27,160 --> 00:14:28,390
if she accepts rent reduction,
interest cuts,

382
00:14:28,390 --> 00:14:29,800
and permanent tenancy rights—

383
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:31,350
yet you're already set on punishing her?

384
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:32,560
Bullshit!

385
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:36,770
After all these years of my father and me
breaking our backs on that land—

386
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:38,110
she just took it back like that?

387
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:40,040
Starving me and my mother out?

388
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,530
I begged her so much,

389
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:43,040
but she wouldn't even
give us one more year.

390
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,960
How is she any better than Pan Xiaogui?

391
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,290
Isn't that an evil deed?

392
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,210
Enough.

393
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,900
All this useless hesitation!

394
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:50,360
If you keep second-guessing,

395
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:52,080
you'll never get anything done—
you'll never lead!

396
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,830
When we act, we act now.

397
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:55,890
Tonight, we will do it!

398
00:14:56,930 --> 00:14:59,160
This is the Farmers' Association's
first big move—

399
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,830
