in this village.

403
00:15:06,380 --> 00:15:08,800
All of them!
We fight for permanent tenancy—

404
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:09,960
so every man can eat his fill

405
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,020
and live decently!

406
00:15:12,470 --> 00:15:13,000
Alright,

407
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:14,210
