496
00:18:35,470 --> 00:18:35,920
Yep.

497
00:18:37,310 --> 00:18:39,920
I heard Pan Xiaogui was denounced
by the Farmers' Association.

498
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:42,120
Now, Pan did some wicked things,

499
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:44,150
but you're nothing like him.

500
00:18:45,030 --> 00:18:45,990
Thing is...

501
00:18:47,310 --> 00:18:49,710
Spit it out!
Quit dancing around the point.

502
00:18:50,780 --> 00:18:52,250
