503
00:18:52,250 --> 00:18:53,490
Tietou and his lot

504
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:55,470
have riled up many tenants.

505
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,030
They're saying

506
00:18:57,290 --> 00:18:58,790
if you don't agree
to lower rents, cut interest,

507
00:18:58,790 --> 00:19:00,400
and grant permanent tenancy—

508
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:02,990
well, it won't matter
if you're a good landlord or not.

509
00:19:02,990 --> 00:19:05,390
They'll make an example of you
all the same.

510
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,270
Who told you this?

511
00:19:09,090 --> 00:19:11,090
Or were you sent to say it to me?

512
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:13,120
No, no.

513
00:19:13,580 --> 00:19:16,000
I'm just worried for you
and the young master—

514
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,400
for our whole Fei family.

515
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:19,400
Surely you understand—

516
00:19:19,570 --> 00:19:22,200
those farmhands won't lift a finger
unless there's profit in it.

517
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:25,330
When they smell gain,
they pounce like starving wolves.

518
00:19:25,790 --> 00:19:27,390
Think carefully about this.

519
00:19:28,470 --> 00:19:29,270
You may go now.

520
00:19:35,010 --> 00:19:36,380
Tietou's first target

521
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:37,920
is Mrs. Fei—that's plain as day.

522
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:40,160
This is about revenge!

523
00:19:40,550 --> 00:19:43,280
He's never forgiven her
for taking back the land.

524
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:45,920
Now he's rallying

525
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:48,200
every farmhand in the village,

526
00:19:48,570 --> 00:19:50,700
especially tenants of the Fei family,

527
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:53,580
demanding permanent tenancy,
rent reduction, and interest cut.

528
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:55,160
If this mob gets out of hand...

529
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,960
it'll be another

530
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,650
Pan Xiaogui struggle session,

531
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,820
and Mrs. Fei won't stand a chance!

532
00:20:02,490 --> 00:20:03,490
Then what do we do?

533
00:20:03,710 --> 00:20:05,440
Should I go warn the Fei family?

534
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:08,510
If Tietou sees you,
he'll hold grudge against you.

535
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:10,640
Mrs. Fei isn't a bad person,

536
00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:12,650
I truly think we ought to help her.

537
00:20:14,470 --> 00:20:16,930
I went to Xiazhuang Village
this afternoon.

538
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,260
