543
00:20:29,710 --> 00:20:31,120
we split up.

544
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:32,980
You go talk some sense into Tietou first.

545
00:20:32,980 --> 00:20:34,110
That's impossible.

546
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:36,730
No use talking!
He won't listen to reason now!

547
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:39,630
