He's at the table.

551
00:21:21,340 --> 00:21:23,010
Come on! Fill Boss's cup.

552
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:24,270
Boss!

553
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:25,510
Boss!

554
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:26,150
Kejin.

555
00:21:28,430 --> 00:21:30,430
Dajiao, what a rare guest!

556
00:21:30,470 --> 00:21:32,200
Come, sit down—
keep me company for a drink!

557
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,200
I'm not drinking.

558
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:34,790
Would you please move your step here?

559
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:35,390
What's up?

560
00:21:36,350 --> 00:21:38,360
Come here please.
I need to tell you something.

561
00:21:38,360 --> 00:21:39,200
Now that you're here,

562
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:40,460
we'll talk right here!

563
00:21:40,670 --> 00:21:41,930
The rest of you, scram.

564
00:21:42,740 --> 00:21:43,840
Let's go in—go in and play!

565
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:44,750
-Go in.
-Come on.

566
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:46,280
Dajiao, have some peanuts.

567
00:21:46,810 --> 00:21:48,140
Have some peanuts here.

568
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,250
You're such a rare gest.

569
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:53,270
What brings you here?

570
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:57,120
Kejin, you know about
the Farmers' Association, don't you?

571
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:58,430
I've heard some things...

572
00:21:58,430 --> 00:21:59,050
What's going on?

573
00:21:59,050 --> 00:22:01,250
Does Ning Xuexiang know about this too?

574
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:03,710
Xiuxiu didn't teach you any manners!

575
00:22:03,710 --> 00:22:04,710
Ning Xuexiang?

576
00:22:04,990 --> 00:22:06,550
Would it kill you to call him Father?

577
00:22:06,550 --> 00:22:08,550
Now's not the right time for this!

578
00:22:09,770 --> 00:22:10,910
Xiuxiu hasn't said anything,

579
00:22:10,910 --> 00:22:12,110
but I know

580
00:22:12,450 --> 00:22:13,710
she's sick with worry!

581
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:14,600
What's she worried about?

582
00:22:14,600 --> 00:22:15,730
Xiuxiu's terrified

583
00:22:16,190 --> 00:22:17,160
that the Farmers' Association

584
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:18,920
will target Father next—

585
00:22:19,420 --> 00:22:20,660
forcing him to

586
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:22,030
reduce rents, cut interest,
and grant permanent tenancy.

587
00:22:22,030 --> 00:22:24,120
She has no idea
if Father will agree on that.

588
00:22:24,120 --> 00:22:24,520
Kejin,

589
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:25,790
at a time like this,

590
00:22:25,790 --> 00:22:27,710
you must convince him not to resist.

591
00:22:27,710 --> 00:22:29,680
Don't let him cling to those things!

592
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:31,680
This afternoon in Xiazhuang...

593
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:33,820
you know the Landlord Pan?

594
00:22:34,030 --> 00:22:35,160
Pan Xiaogui, right?

595
00:22:35,310 --> 00:22:36,310
He's richer than our father,

596
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:37,600
with more land.

597
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:38,650
What happened?

598
00:22:38,990 --> 00:22:40,990
He refused
the Farmers' Association demands.

599
00:22:40,990 --> 00:22:42,320
So they dragged him out.

600
00:22:43,250 --> 00:22:44,620
Tenants lined up

601
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:47,030
to expose his crimes—

602
00:22:47,230 --> 00:22:49,030
rotting vegetables, eggs

603
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,450
to the face.

604
00:22:50,470 --> 00:22:51,550
He broke fast.

605
00:22:52,160 --> 00:22:53,580
At last he agreed to everything.

606
00:22:53,580 --> 00:22:55,750
He agreed to reduce rents,
cut interest rates,

607
00:22:55,750 --> 00:22:58,210
and grant permanent tenancy
to the farmers.

608
00:22:58,750 --> 00:22:59,550
Our village

609
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:00,950
won't see trouble.

610
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:05,560
No Pan Xiaogui here,

611
00:23:06,230 --> 00:23:08,090
no Farmers' Association either.

612
00:23:08,270 --> 00:23:09,680
Who'd dare make waves?

613
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:11,820
Everyone knows the stakes!

614
00:23:11,820 --> 00:23:12,820
This whole thing?

615
00:23:12,840 --> 00:23:15,900
Like picking coins
straight from a landlord's pocket!

616
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:17,860
Isn't it so?

617
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:19,060
Go tell Xiuxiu:

618
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:20,030
Rest easy.

619
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,070
I'm here—

620
00:23:21,270 --> 00:23:22,670
Father won't lose a hair.

621
00:23:23,070 --> 00:23:23,470
Kejin,

622
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:25,400
you really think

623
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:27,030
no one dares to try this?

624
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:29,360
Don't tell me you're behind this, Dajiao!

625
00:23:30,770 --> 00:23:32,090
Pretend I never spoke!

626
00:23:32,470 --> 00:23:33,990
Kejin, for Xiuxiu's sake—

627
00:23:33,990 --> 00:23:36,050
talk some sense into Father. I'm out.

628
00:23:37,790 --> 00:23:38,790
Go tell my sister—

629
00:23:39,060 --> 00:23:40,060
I got the message.

630
00:23:48,070 --> 00:23:48,710
Tietou!

631
00:23:49,990 --> 00:23:50,470
Tietou!

632
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:52,790
I've got something important to tell you.

633
00:23:52,790 --> 00:23:54,050
What is it? Spit it out.

634
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:55,360
This concerns your big plans.

635
00:23:55,360 --> 00:23:57,090
Are you gonna hear me properly?

636
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:01,210
Fine. Talk.

637
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:05,230
I've been thinking about your big plan.

638
00:24:06,780 --> 00:24:09,180
You can't just target
the Fei family first!

639
00:24:09,710 --> 00:24:10,230
Why not?

640
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:12,960
You need to gain trust first.

641
00:24:13,990 --> 00:24:14,710
Gain trust?

642
00:24:14,990 --> 00:24:16,390
What exactly do you mean?

643
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,910
To achieve great things,

644
00:24:18,070 --> 00:24:18,960
you must make

645
00:24:19,230 --> 00:24:20,160
your followers

646
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,550
obey you willingly,

647
00:24:21,580 --> 00:24:23,120
follow you wholeheartedly.

648
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:26,180
This is how you truly command
the people's allegiance.

649
00:24:26,630 --> 00:24:27,460
Fair point.

650
00:24:28,420 --> 00:24:29,680
Sure, my four childhood buddies and you—

651
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:31,560
you're all willing to follow me, right?

652
00:24:31,560 --> 00:24:32,600
Fine.

653
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:34,270
But here's the problem:

654
00:24:34,270 --> 00:24:35,990
If we target the Fei Family first,

655
00:24:35,990 --> 00:24:37,160
everyone will say

656
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:39,510
Tietou's exploiting his position
for personal revenge.

657
00:24:39,510 --> 00:24:43,160
They'll claim you're using
the Farmers' Association for own agenda.

658
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:43,880
Wait, what?

659
00:24:44,270 --> 00:24:46,880
Think carefully:

660
00:24:47,750 --> 00:24:48,880
If Mrs. Fei caves—

661
00:24:49,360 --> 00:24:51,360
agreeing to rent reductions,
interest cuts,

662
00:24:51,360 --> 00:24:53,030
and permanent tenancy—what then?

663
00:24:53,030 --> 00:24:54,690
Once people connect the dots,

664
00:24:54,710 --> 00:24:56,120
they'll realize you manipulated
the Farmers' Association

665
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:57,790
for vengeance.

666
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,840
And when word gets out?

667
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:01,920
Will your men still trust you?

668
00:25:02,360 --> 00:25:04,070
Will they follow you willingly?

669
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:05,880
More importantly, if that spreads out,

670
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,990
will Mr. Bai—

671
00:25:08,470 --> 00:25:10,120
who appointed you
as head of the Farmers' Association—

672
00:25:10,120 --> 00:25:11,710
and the other officials

673
00:25:12,070 --> 00:25:13,510
still have faith in you?

674
00:25:16,770 --> 00:25:17,570
You're right.

675
00:25:18,610 --> 00:25:19,610
That makes sense.

676
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:22,030
Look, I won't lie—

677
00:25:22,030 --> 00:25:24,030
all I want is to crush that old widow.

678
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:26,880
But if you're saying

679
00:25:27,710 --> 00:25:29,270
I need the people's trust first...

680
00:25:29,270 --> 00:25:30,750
then I can't touch her yet.

681
00:25:31,120 --> 00:25:31,650
Alright.

682
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,290
Let me think on this.

683
00:25:33,990 --> 00:25:35,030
My advice?

684
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:37,260
Gather all the village landlords

685
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:39,710
for a meeting.

686
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:41,830
First, ask who's willing to

687
00:25:42,120 --> 00:25:44,180
voluntarily reduce rent, cut interest,

688
00:25:44,180 --> 00:25:45,510
and grant permanent tenancy—

689
00:25:45,510 --> 00:25:47,510
start with diplomacy before force.

690
00:25:49,270 --> 00:25:50,640
And Xiuxiu has got a big surprise

691
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,720
for your Farmers' Association!

692
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:54,610
What's that?

693
00:25:55,210 --> 00:25:56,230
She swore me to secrecy…

694
00:25:56,230 --> 00:25:57,690
you'll find out tomorrow.

695
00:25:58,510 --> 00:26:00,230
Cut the suspense—what's this big surprise

696
00:26:00,230 --> 00:26:01,790
that has to wait till dawn?

697
00:26:01,820 --> 00:26:03,020
Wait overnight then.

698
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:05,130
Let the anticipation kill you.

699
00:26:07,670 --> 00:26:08,120
Okay.

700
00:26:09,830 --> 00:26:13,450
Fine!

701
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,330
To win the crowd,

702
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:16,980
I'll spare the old widow—for now.

703
00:26:16,980 --> 00:26:20,580
But your father-in-law, Ning Xuexiang?
He's first on the block!

704
00:26:35,710 --> 00:26:36,400
Xiuxiu!

705
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:37,120
Go! Move it!

706
00:26:37,120 --> 00:26:38,680
-Xiuxiu.
-Father.

707
00:26:38,710 --> 00:26:39,360
Go! hurry up.

708
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:41,030
Xiu—Xiuxiu.

709
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:43,070
Move it! Accept your punishment! Hurry up.

710
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:43,640
Father.

711
00:27:25,600 --> 00:27:25,960
Xiu.

712
00:27:27,310 --> 00:27:28,160
Sister-in-law.

713
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:29,160
it's late—

714
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:30,420
where are you heading?

715
00:27:31,040 --> 00:27:31,810
Sister-in-law,

716
00:27:31,810 --> 00:27:33,600
what's that in your hand?

717
00:27:35,650 --> 00:27:38,450
I'm on my way to deliver a message
to Ning Xuexiang.

718
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:41,680
See?

719
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:42,890
Did you see that?

720
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:44,200
This... this is their landlord's familuy!

721
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:45,880
Look at your wife!

722
00:27:45,910 --> 00:27:46,780
No yelling!

723
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:50,740
Go to him now?
What are you talking about?

724
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:53,490
Don't you already know what I'm gonna say?

725
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:54,360
What?

726
00:27:54,990 --> 00:27:55,550
Dajiao!

727
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,250
You knew about this too—

728
00:27:58,540 --> 00:28:00,000
knew what the letter said.

729
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:01,760
After all my trust in you!

730
00:28:02,330 --> 00:28:03,680
I barely finished telling you at home,

731
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:04,780
and by the time you came back from supper,

732
00:28:04,780 --> 00:28:06,070
you'd already blabbed to your wife?

733
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:07,710
You—unbelievable!

734
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:09,270
Have you forgotten who you are?

735
00:28:09,270 --> 00:28:10,550
You're a farmhand!

736
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:12,160
Not one of their damn landlords!

737
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:12,640
Tietou—

738
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,600
if you really wanna know,

739
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,920
see for yourself.

740
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,030
-I can't read.
-Brother.

741
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:25,030
What brother?

742
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:27,290
It's Director Tietou.

743
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:28,640
-What?
-Director.

744
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:29,230
Let me

745
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:30,200
report our assembled numbers

746
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,070
to you.

747
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:32,840
Your business can wait.

748
00:28:32,990 --> 00:28:34,430
Read this letter to me—now.

749
00:28:34,430 --> 00:28:34,990
Quickly!

750
00:28:38,710 --> 00:28:39,170
Baisui.

751
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:41,470
As if I can read.

752
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:42,490
You read it!

753
00:28:46,160 --> 00:28:50,120
You must've heard by now.

754
00:28:50,630 --> 00:28:51,890
Kn—Know what?

755
00:28:53,520 --> 00:28:56,320
I can't read the next word.
That's all I recognize.

756
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,530
None of you can read!

757
00:28:57,980 --> 00:28:59,290
I, I can read...

758
00:28:59,310 --> 00:29:00,840
I can even write my own name!

759
00:29:01,990 --> 00:29:03,120
I'll read it for you.

760
00:29:05,670 --> 00:29:06,330
You read it.

761
00:29:06,770 --> 00:29:07,770
Quickly! Read it!

762
00:29:09,520 --> 00:29:10,520
What I wrote is:

763
00:29:11,710 --> 00:29:13,960
You must know about
the Farmers' Association by now.

764
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,020
You must have known

765
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:15,990
that this Farmers' Association helps

766
00:29:15,990 --> 00:29:17,680
farmhands demand

767
00:29:17,710 --> 00:29:18,990
permanent tenancy,

768
00:29:19,360 --> 00:29:20,920
rent cuts, and lower interest.

769
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:22,810
I won't lecture you;

770
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:24,930
you understand the stakes.

771
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:27,840
The time has come for landlords to act.

772
00:29:29,120 --> 00:29:31,150
When you refused to sell land to free me,

773
00:29:31,150 --> 00:29:32,670
you only broke my heart.

774
00:29:33,590 --> 00:29:36,180
But if you resist

775
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,880
the Farmers' Association's terms now,

776
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:39,210
you'll become the enemy

777
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,790
of every tenant, every laborer—

778
00:29:40,790 --> 00:29:42,550
tenant farmers.

779
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:44,530
just like Pan Xiaogui.

780
00:29:45,030 --> 00:29:45,760
That's a role

781
00:29:47,570 --> 00:29:48,700
I beg you not to play.

782
00:29:51,990 --> 00:29:52,850
It's finished.

783
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:54,070
No lies?

784
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:56,250
If you don't believe me,

785
00:29:56,310 --> 00:29:58,410
find someone who can read
and have them repeat it to you.

786
00:29:58,410 --> 00:30:00,010
I'm going to Fourth Grandpa.

787
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,200
I dare you to lie to me.

788
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:06,230
Even if you didn't deliver
the letter to Ning Xuexiang,

789
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:07,640
your advice means nothing.

790
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,100
We don't need your advice.

791
00:30:09,160 --> 00:30:12,680
The Farmers' Association's business

792
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:13,840
is ours to decide—

793
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,420
no outsiders get a say.

794
00:30:17,470 --> 00:30:18,330
Fine! Someone—

795
00:30:19,230 --> 00:30:19,960
keep watch.

796
00:30:20,050 --> 00:30:21,600
Don't let her leave this house.

797
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:22,160
Tietou,

798
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:23,680
you're crossing a line.

799
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:25,550
Don't flaunt petty authority
like it's imperial decree!

800
00:30:25,550 --> 00:30:26,750
Why guard her?

801
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,310
After all your sister-in-law did—

802
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:29,310
even embroidering banners for you?

803
00:30:29,310 --> 00:30:30,440
Ungrateful wretch.

804
00:30:30,850 --> 00:30:32,320
Flag? What flag?

805
00:30:33,560 --> 00:30:36,760
I want to embroider a flag
for your Farmers' Association.

806
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:38,360
I know

807
00:30:38,600 --> 00:30:40,200
you started this Farmers' Association

808
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:42,070
to speak up for the farmhands,

809
00:30:42,270 --> 00:30:43,200
to stand by them,

810
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:45,160
to give them a better life.

811
00:30:46,310 --> 00:30:47,510
I admire you for that,

812
00:30:47,810 --> 00:30:49,140
and I've been thinking…

813
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:50,510
how can I help?

814
00:30:51,650 --> 00:30:53,120
So I'd like to stitch a flag
for your Farmers' Association—

815
00:30:53,120 --> 00:30:54,720
something you can raise high

816
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:56,500
when you rally

817
00:30:56,530 --> 00:30:58,530
for the farmhands,

818
00:30:58,550 --> 00:31:00,480
when you stand up for their rights.

819
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:06,160
Great!

820
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:07,560
Very good!

821
00:31:09,310 --> 00:31:11,370
You can keep embroidering your flag,

822
00:31:11,470 --> 00:31:12,790
but my work won't stop.

823
00:31:13,710 --> 00:31:14,710
Especially now—

824
00:31:14,740 --> 00:31:17,200
this is when we can't afford
a single misstep.

825
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:17,730
Alright,

826
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:19,920
Then I'll trouble you

827
00:31:20,310 --> 00:31:22,440
to go inside and embroider the banner.

828
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:25,270
You'd better go keep watch.

829
00:31:25,270 --> 00:31:26,740
Until we've fully assembled,

830
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:27,780
don't let her out.

831
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:28,660
Roger that!

832
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:32,070
Who gave you the right
to watch my daughter-in-law?

833
00:31:32,070 --> 00:31:33,150
One night without oversight,

834
00:31:33,150 --> 00:31:34,870
and you thinks you're the law?

835
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:36,120
If he dares to

836
00:31:36,470 --> 00:31:39,030
lay a finger on Xiuxiu—

837
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:40,790
I'll break his legs myself!

838
00:31:40,790 --> 00:31:41,400
Save it.

839
00:31:42,230 --> 00:31:43,890
What do you two old folks know?

840
00:31:44,360 --> 00:31:45,600
Get inside. Keep watch for me.

841
00:31:45,600 --> 00:31:45,960
To my place. Come on—let's talk business.

842
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,760
Dajiao. You don't get involved.

843
00:31:48,140 --> 00:31:49,290
You just wait!

844
00:31:49,310 --> 00:31:50,030
Easy.

845
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:51,660
Father,

846
00:31:51,990 --> 00:31:53,590
I still need to get involved.

847
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,340
I'll explain to you later.

848
00:31:58,680 --> 00:31:59,680
Director Tietou,

849
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,360
our squad's assembled—

850
00:32:01,830 --> 00:32:03,660
near Wu San's place in Xiawa.

851
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:06,110
We have 13 men in total.

852
00:32:08,470 --> 00:32:09,840
My squad's not ready;

853
00:32:09,990 --> 00:32:11,590
a few backed out last minute.

854
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,790
There are only 7 now.

855
00:32:15,160 --> 00:32:16,020
What happened?

856
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:19,780
Some say they're tired from a day's work—

857
00:32:20,270 --> 00:32:21,870
some haven't even eaten yet,

858
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:24,510
others finished dinnerr
and turned in early

859
00:32:24,510 --> 00:32:26,970
to save strength for tomorrow's fieldwork.

860
00:32:27,030 --> 00:32:28,290
And those hired hands?

861
00:32:28,550 --> 00:32:30,410
They wouldn't dare be late at all.

862
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:33,030
After all I've done for them,

863
00:32:33,750 --> 00:32:34,510
all they care about

864
00:32:34,510 --> 00:32:35,840
is eating and sleeping?

865
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:37,360
If we succeed,

866
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:38,970
their lives will improve—

867
00:32:39,270 --> 00:32:40,470
can't they grasp that?

868
00:32:40,470 --> 00:32:41,840
Still acting like hired hands?

869
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,170
Go! Round them up again!

870
00:32:43,840 --> 00:32:46,010
There were 60 to 70
took our tokens this morning—

871
00:32:46,010 --> 00:32:47,750
anyone who took one
is a Farmers' Association member now!

872
00:32:47,750 --> 00:32:48,750
They have to join!

873
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:49,880
Make it clear:

874
00:32:50,310 --> 00:32:51,360
I, Feng Tietou, am here

875
00:32:51,360 --> 00:32:52,510
to back them!

876
00:32:53,030 --> 00:32:55,270
Every grievance, every humiliation
from the landlords,

877
00:32:55,270 --> 00:32:56,510
we'll make it right—

878
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:57,740
if they stand with us!

879
00:32:58,030 --> 00:32:59,400
Act like a real captain!

880
00:32:59,750 --> 00:33:01,680
Alright, I'll give it another try.

881
00:33:03,070 --> 00:33:04,690
Zhiquan. How many people do you have?

882
00:33:04,690 --> 00:33:06,530
I have the same as Baisui's group.

883
00:33:06,530 --> 00:33:07,920
I have only 8 people.

884
00:33:08,230 --> 00:33:09,410
I only have 4 here.

885
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:12,290
I only handed out 6 tokens all morning.

886
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:15,030
How many people do you have again?

887
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:15,830
I have 13 here.

888
00:33:19,360 --> 00:33:21,890
What can a handful of people
even accomplish?

889
00:33:22,790 --> 00:33:25,640
Look at how we took down Pan Xiaogui—
that crowd, that energy!

890
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:27,640
That made an impact! That got heard!

891
00:33:28,610 --> 00:33:29,680
Hold on, Director,

892
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:33,000
aren't we going to the Fei Residence?

893
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:34,550
Only her,

894
00:33:34,840 --> 00:33:36,510
the Ning family's second daughter,

895
00:33:36,510 --> 00:33:37,770
and Fei Wendian there—

896
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:39,570
we're just giving them a scare!

897
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:40,970
We're more than enough.

898
00:33:41,840 --> 00:33:42,360
No.

899
00:33:43,230 --> 00:33:44,510
Forget the old widow—

900
00:33:45,120 --> 00:33:46,980
we're going after Ning Xuexiang!

901
00:33:47,030 --> 00:33:48,040
Going after whom?

902
00:33:48,420 --> 00:33:49,550
Ning Xuexiang.

903
00:33:51,790 --> 00:33:53,120
Do you all think

904
00:33:53,380 --> 00:33:54,640
I became head of the Farmers' Association

905
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:55,700
just for myself?

906
00:33:57,790 --> 00:33:59,030
That none of you truly respect me?

907
00:33:59,030 --> 00:33:59,840
No!

908
00:33:59,870 --> 00:34:00,740
No?

909
00:34:00,990 --> 00:34:02,850
We're taking down Ning Xuexiang.

910
00:34:05,790 --> 00:34:06,710
Now, none of you disrespect me, do you?

911
00:34:06,710 --> 00:34:07,270
We won't.

912
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:10,030
At first light,

913
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,830
we march—no matter how many show up.

914
00:34:11,830 --> 00:34:12,350
Baisui,

915
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,110
take a few men

916
00:34:14,110 --> 00:34:15,639
and block the village gate.

917
00:34:16,110 --> 00:34:17,510
No one warns Ning Kejin.

918
00:34:18,510 --> 00:34:18,880
Okay.

919
00:34:19,239 --> 00:34:20,960
Once we've dealt with
the richest landlord in this village,

920
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:22,070
the rest will fall like dominos.

921
00:34:22,070 --> 00:34:22,800
I'll join you

922
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:24,239
to gather people.

923
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:26,400
I refuse to believe this is how it ends!
Move, move!

924
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,989
What's the rush?

925
00:34:28,810 --> 00:34:30,719
Xiuxiu can't finish embroidering

926
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:32,389
that banner overnight.

927
00:34:32,710 --> 00:34:34,840
Are you just giving up on your squad now?

928
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:36,090
If she finishes it, we'll use it.

929
00:34:36,090 --> 00:34:37,949
If not, we march without waiting.

930
00:34:38,510 --> 00:34:39,989
Let fate decide.

931
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:41,590
Move out!

932
00:34:52,469 --> 00:34:53,190
Xiu.

933
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:55,760
Mother,

934
00:34:55,989 --> 00:34:57,450
why aren't you asleep yet?

935
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,150
With all this chaos,

936
00:34:59,150 --> 00:35:01,190
how can your father and I sleep?

937
00:35:01,890 --> 00:35:03,690
I made you some millet porridge.

938
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:05,790
Thank you, Mother.

939
00:35:05,790 --> 00:35:06,790
Warm yourself up.

940
00:35:09,680 --> 00:35:11,360
Have some more. It's millet porriage.

941
00:35:11,360 --> 00:35:12,560
I'll drink it in a bit.

942
00:35:14,630 --> 00:35:15,280
Xiu,

943
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:16,740
This embroidery of yours—

944
00:35:17,240 --> 00:35:18,760
fine work!

945
00:35:20,660 --> 00:35:22,270
Xiu, you're so talented!

946
00:35:27,880 --> 00:35:31,150
Tietou's doing this for us farmhands—
for our own good.

947
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:32,280
That...

948
00:35:32,730 --> 00:35:34,390
Farmers' Association thing,

949
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:36,590
I can't stomach

950
00:35:36,590 --> 00:35:37,880
how Tietou's acting

951
00:35:38,030 --> 00:35:39,670
all high and mighty—

952
00:35:39,980 --> 00:35:42,380
like a toad
pretending to ride a palanquin!

953
00:35:42,560 --> 00:35:44,920
You're here embroidering his flag,

954
00:35:44,950 --> 00:35:46,750
yet he posts guards to watch you!

955
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:51,160
Xiuxiu... it's not easy for you.

956
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:54,730
You're stuck between
the landlords' kin on one side,

957
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:57,070
and us farmhands on the other.

958
00:35:57,510 --> 00:35:59,030
How do you navigate this?

959
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:00,910
Tell me!

960
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:02,150
Mother.

961
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:04,490
You're the one who gets me.

962
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:07,470
Didn't Tietou himself say—

963
00:36:07,470 --> 00:36:09,880
might not even use the flag?

964
00:36:10,030 --> 00:36:12,960
Yet you're rushing yourself to stitch it?

965
00:36:14,650 --> 00:36:16,850
Right now, I don't want to overthink it.

966
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,980
I just want to embroider this banner—

967
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:22,070
to do my part
for the Farmers' Association.

968
00:36:23,030 --> 00:36:24,190
If I finish it, good.

969
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:25,510
If not…

970
00:36:26,190 --> 00:36:27,720
well, I've put effort.

971
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:37,440
Director.

972
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:39,470
How's the gathering going?

973
00:36:39,470 --> 00:36:40,470
Everyone is here.

974
00:36:40,610 --> 00:36:42,340
Baisui Fei's squad, 27 people.

975
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:44,190
Reporting to Chief Tietou:

976
00:36:44,190 --> 00:36:46,280
Niu Wu's squad, 28 people.

977
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:48,090
Okay... 28 people.

978
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:49,540
Gu Zhiquan's squad, 16 people,

979
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:51,200
Fei Qiansheng's squad has 20.

980
00:36:52,640 --> 00:36:53,150
Great!

981
00:36:54,470 --> 00:36:55,000
Alright.

982
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:57,510
We move out

983
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:58,780
at first light.

984
00:36:58,920 --> 00:36:59,720
Okay.
Good.

985
00:37:00,470 --> 00:37:00,920
San.

986
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:01,880
San!

987
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,280
We're moving out!

988
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:04,070
No more guards!

989
00:37:04,070 --> 00:37:04,630
No more watching?

990
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:05,360
Yes, hurry up and go!

991
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:05,690
Okay.

992
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:11,160
No more watching now?

993
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:15,050
Where are you going?

994
00:37:16,620 --> 00:37:18,940
I'm feeling a bit worried.

995
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:21,880
Look at how Tietou's posturing—

996
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:24,240
he's coming for Ning Xuexiang!

997
00:37:24,650 --> 00:37:25,890
Miser Ning!

998
00:37:26,250 --> 00:37:29,670
I'm getting worried about him.

999
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:31,160
I'd better go check.

1000
00:37:32,690 --> 00:37:33,840
After all, we're in-laws.

1001
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:36,040
We should help out if there's anything.

1002
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:43,960
Mother.

1003
00:37:44,360 --> 00:37:45,150
It's done.

1004
00:37:46,190 --> 00:37:47,110
Let me see.

1005
00:37:57,150 --> 00:37:57,750
It's nice!

1006
00:37:59,240 --> 00:37:59,900
Excellent!

1007
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,290
Sister-in-law.

1008
00:38:03,090 --> 00:38:03,760
I, Feng Tietou, speak for

1009
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:06,690
the Farmers' Association brothers
when I thank you!

1010
00:38:13,890 --> 00:38:16,290
Listen well, brothers of the Association—

1011
00:38:16,790 --> 00:38:18,580
The time has come

1012
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:21,470
for us poor farmhands to stand tall!

1013
00:38:26,110 --> 00:38:27,640
When we face the landlords,

1014
00:38:27,690 --> 00:38:29,220
demand permanent tenancy!

1015
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:31,250
Whoever shouts loudest

1016
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:33,040
gets to negotiate first!

1017
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:35,090
He'll secure his rights first!

1018
00:38:35,110 --> 00:38:37,570
With the Farmers' Association
backing you,

1019
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:38,550
have no fear!

1020
00:38:38,990 --> 00:38:39,840
Today,

1021
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:42,320
we'll head to the Ning Residence first.

1022
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:43,150
Move out!

1023
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:44,720
Move out!

1024
00:38:49,740 --> 00:38:50,760
I'll go along and see what happens.

1025
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:51,780
You go home first,

1026
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:54,130
and I'll let you know
if anything happens.

1027
00:39:04,170 --> 00:39:05,740
Dazi, what are you watching there?

1028
00:39:05,740 --> 00:39:06,700
Come on, join us!

1029
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:10,540
Join the Farmers' Association!
You'll never go hungry!

1030
00:39:10,540 --> 00:39:13,070
-You'll never go hungry!
-You'll never go hungry!

1031
00:39:13,070 --> 00:39:14,700
-Give me a badge!
-Give me a badge!

1032
00:39:14,700 --> 00:39:15,120
Here!

1033
00:39:16,150 --> 00:39:17,590
Join the Farmers' Association!

1034
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:18,740
You'll never go hungry!

1035
00:39:18,740 --> 00:39:20,740
You'll never go hungry!

1036
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:25,320
Join the Farmers' Association!
You'll never go hungry!

1037
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,760
You'll never go hungry!

1038
00:39:30,030 --> 00:39:31,830
Returning from the county town,

1039
00:39:32,070 --> 00:39:34,630
my heart kept swinging

1040
00:39:34,660 --> 00:39:36,320
between hope and dread.
Hope,

1041
00:39:36,720 --> 00:39:38,630
Hope, because Mr. Du spoke of

1042
00:39:38,630 --> 00:39:41,430
how the Farmers' Association
backs us farmhands—

1043
00:39:41,720 --> 00:39:44,720
our future finally brightens.

1044
00:39:45,030 --> 00:39:46,400
But dread...

1045
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:48,360
will Ning Xuexiang
ever voluntarily cut rents,

1046
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:50,960
slash interest,
and grant permanent tenancy?

1047
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:54,770
My mind's in turmoil.

1048
00:39:56,630 --> 00:39:57,760
This is unbearable!

1049
00:39:57,800 --> 00:39:59,960
Tietou has really
established the peasant association,

1050
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:02,020
though this group
looks a bit shabby.

1051
00:40:02,210 --> 00:40:03,760
You've been all over the place.

1052
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:04,730
What do you think?

1053
00:40:04,730 --> 00:40:05,960
Can this succeed?

1054
00:40:06,150 --> 00:40:07,920
I don't quite know about other places,

1055
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:09,390
but if our village wants to succeed,

1056
00:40:09,390 --> 00:40:11,180
Tietou needs to give each one

1057
00:40:11,200 --> 00:40:13,800
a pair of pants
that can cover their backsides.

1058
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:15,440
You bet.

1059
00:40:15,470 --> 00:40:16,200
Pants!

1060
00:40:18,190 --> 00:40:18,990
Humpback Guo.

1061
00:40:19,990 --> 00:40:21,630
Even though
you don't know how to farm,

1062
00:40:21,630 --> 00:40:23,190
our farmers' association
doesn't look down on you..

1063
00:40:23,190 --> 00:40:25,520
Come in, I'll give you a membership badge.

1064
00:40:25,590 --> 00:40:26,590
Thanks, brother.

1065
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:27,920
But I'll pass.

1066
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:30,260
I don't farm, but I have pants to wear.

1067
00:40:31,090 --> 00:40:33,020
And my leather shoes fit just fine.

1068
00:40:34,150 --> 00:40:36,520
You're shortsighted.

1069
00:40:37,690 --> 00:40:38,760
Let that old donkey of yours

1070
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:39,960
keep trudging on!

1071
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:43,840
Next time you beg to join us,
I'll slam the door in your face!

1072
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:44,760
Anyone else?

1073
00:40:45,210 --> 00:40:46,300
It's not too late.

1074
00:40:46,320 --> 00:40:47,920
I'll make you a membership badge.

1075
00:40:47,920 --> 00:40:49,240
Join the Farmers' Association!

1076
00:40:49,240 --> 00:40:50,280
You'll never go hungry!

1077
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:52,510
Join the Farmers' Association!
You'll never go hungry!

1078
00:40:52,510 --> 00:40:53,320
Tietou!

1079
00:40:53,320 --> 00:40:54,650
Zhuzi wants to join too.

1080
00:40:54,660 --> 00:40:54,990
Go on!

1081
00:40:54,990 --> 00:40:56,050
When did I say that?

1082
00:40:56,470 --> 00:40:57,070
Go, go!

1083
00:40:57,630 --> 00:40:58,400
Come and get your badge.

1084
00:40:58,400 --> 00:40:59,330
Make him a badge.

1085
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:02,370
Let's go!

1086
00:41:02,940 --> 00:41:04,380
Count me in!

1087
00:41:37,110 --> 00:41:38,030
Everyone!

1088
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:38,840
Yes!

1089
00:41:39,470 --> 00:41:40,630
Start drilling!

1090
00:41:50,550 --> 00:41:52,210
Shall we just forget about it?

1091
00:41:54,570 --> 00:41:55,820
They're gone.

1092
00:41:57,500 --> 00:41:58,460
Are you a coward?

1093
00:41:59,070 --> 00:42:00,330
All of you are cowards.

1094
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:04,400
Brothers, get your weapons!

1095
00:42:04,470 --> 00:42:05,240
Yes, sir!

1096
00:42:06,880 --> 00:42:07,880
Brothers!

1097
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:08,880
We're here!

1098
00:42:09,210 --> 00:42:10,890
Since our Ox Temple militia

1099
00:42:10,960 --> 00:42:12,400
was formed,

1100
00:42:12,860 --> 00:42:14,530
it's won countless merits.

1101
00:42:14,920 --> 00:42:15,920
We protect homes

1102
00:42:16,860 --> 00:42:18,130
from bandits,

1103
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:20,190
hunt thieves,

1104
00:42:20,900 --> 00:42:22,470
and guard this land's peace!

1105
00:42:22,470 --> 00:42:23,720
To troublemakers—

1106
00:42:24,110 --> 00:42:24,840
what do we do?

1107
00:42:24,940 --> 00:42:27,090
Beat them till none return!

1108
00:42:27,190 --> 00:42:30,020
To those who bully the weak
or defy authority—what do we do?

1109
00:42:30,020 --> 00:42:32,080
